Class SequenceDiagramWriter

java.lang.Object
  org.aoplib4j.uml.SequenceDiagramWriter
Direct Known Subclasses:
DFSDiagramWriter
public abstract class SequenceDiagramWriter
extends java.lang.Object

Root class for all the sequence diagram writers. This class contains a writer that will be used to write the diagram.

Author:
Adrian Citu
